org.plasma.runtime.annotation

Annotation Type NamespaceProvisioning


  • @Target(value=PACKAGE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface NamespaceProvisioning
    Specifies various provisioning properties within the context of a namespace.
     

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String rootPackageName
      The qualified Java package for generated interfaces for this namespace.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      EnumSource enumSource
      When logical property names are generated and/or referenced as enums within generated code, specifies how enums are originated
      java.lang.String implementationClassNamePrefix
      The string to prepend to implementation class names
      java.lang.String implementationClassNameSuffix
      The string to append to implementation class names
      java.lang.String implementationPackageName
      The name of the child or sub package for implementation classes for this provisioning context
      java.lang.String interfaceNamePrefix
      The string to prepend to interface class names
      java.lang.String interfaceNameSuffix
      The string to append to interface class names
      PropertyNameStyle propertyNameStyle
      Specifies how logical property names are generated and referenced within SDO interfaces and implementation classes.
      java.lang.String queryDSLClassNamePrefix
      The string to prepend to Query DSL class names
      java.lang.String queryDSLClassNameSuffix
      The string to append to Query DSL class names
      boolean queryDSLGenerate
      Whether to generate Query DSL classes for this context
      java.lang.String queryDSLPackageName
      The name of the child or sub package for Query DSL classes for this provisioning context
